item.title: By: monica
item.dc:creator: monica
item.description: You just peeped into the alternate reality, and one of it's many exciting features is the "nano hand foam"... whoda thunk? What with the hummer nano, the ipod nano, and so forth...I really have to finish my script on nanotechnology before the rest of the people sharing the creative "oversoul" already finish their drafts!!!
